loses cash - I know its annoying, and my manual is getting
messed with all the opening etc, but its an effective technique
to overcome simple pirating.

Take it this way: most games prompt at the beginning, just
phone the mate you copied from, and hey - leave the machine
on all day. Frontier is the kind of game that can be played
all day.

